<template>
  <button class="flex font-extrabold" @click="this.setShowLeftBar()">
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      fill="none"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      stroke-width="1.5"
      stroke="currentColor"
      class="w-8 h-8"
    >
      <path
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        d="M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25h16.5"
      />
    </svg>
  </button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "HamburgerMenuIcon",
  methods: {
    setShowLeftBar() {
      this.$store.commit("setShowLeftBar");
    },
  },
};
</script>
